sentences.english: Terminals installed with the freestanding structure, with connection part sub-installment structure, metal casing, is easy to install.
sentences.chinese: 独立式带接线端子安装结构，金属外壳，便于安装。

sentences.english: The metal shells of all mechanic equipments should be well connected to PE line.
sentences.chinese: 所有机电设备的金属外壳必须与保护零线做可靠联接。

sentences.english: Metal skins will be welded together with lasers, eliminating thousands of fasteners.
sentences.chinese: 金属外壳由激光铎成一体，从而免去成千上万个扣钉。

sentences.english: Its body flips and spins, guarding itself with its altogether more sturdy metal casing.
sentences.chinese: 它不断翻动和旋转，用更坚固的金属外壳保护自己。

sentences.english: Even if you touch the metal of your car it's actually better than not touching it.
sentences.chinese: 就算摸摸车的金属外壳也不错，比你完全不碰它更好。

sentences.english: Such designs can compensate for slight aberrations in the placement of the metal shell.
sentences.chinese: 如此设计可代偿放置金属外壳时的轻微偏差。

sentences.english: Oakley's got you covered either way with the Full Metal Jacket.
sentences.chinese: 这款奥克利全金属外壳能让你不再犹豫。
